=== WRITING PATTERN INSTRUCTIONS ===

MIRROR THESE EXACT PATTERNS:

SENTENCE STRUCTURE:
- Average length: {{round patterns.sentencePatterns.avgLength 1}} words
- Short sentences (<10 words): {{percent patterns.sentencePatterns.distribution.short}}%
- Medium sentences (10-25 words): {{percent patterns.sentencePatterns.distribution.medium}}%
- Long sentences (>25 words): {{percent patterns.sentencePatterns.distribution.long}}%

PARAGRAPH STRUCTURE:
{{#each patterns.paragraphPatterns}}
- {{this.type}}: {{this.percentage}}% - {{this.description}}
{{/each}}

OPENINGS (use exactly as shown):
{{#each patterns.openingPatterns}}
- "{{{this.pattern}}}" ({{percent this.frequency}}%){{#if this.notes}} - {{{this.notes}}}{{/if}}
{{/each}}

VALEDICTIONS (closing phrases):
{{#each patterns.valediction}}
- {{{this.phrase}}} ({{this.percentage}}%)
{{/each}}

TYPED NAME FORMATS:
{{#each patterns.typedName}}
- {{{this.phrase}}} ({{this.percentage}}%)
{{/each}}

NEVER DO THESE THINGS:
{{#if patterns.negativePatterns.length}}
{{#each patterns.negativePatterns}}
